peru consum price rise 5.3 pct in march peru 's consuemr price index rose 5.3 pct last month to 13,914.4 ( base 100 ) follow a 5.3 pct increas in februari and 5.3 pct rise in march 1986 , the nation statist institut said . it said that the accumul inflat for the first three month of 1987 wa 18.5 pct compar to 15.4 pct for the same period last year . inflat for the 12-month period end march 1987 wa 67.4 pct compar to 120.8 pct for the 12-month period end march 1986 .